gst-launch-1.0.exe filesrc location=test_input.mp4 ! qtdemux ! h264parse ! mp4mux streamable=true fragment-duration=1000 ! filesink location=out3/out.mp4

- generates fragmented file

gst-launch-1.0.exe filesrc location=test_input.mp4 ! qtdemux ! h264parse ! splitmuxsink location=out3/video%02d.mp4 muxer-factory=mp4mux muxer-properties="properties,streamable=true,fragment-duration=1000" async-finalize=true

- does not generate fragmented file

 gst-launch-1.0.exe filesrc location=test_input.mp4 ! qtdemux ! h264parse ! splitmuxsink location=out3/video%02d.mp4 muxer-factory=mp4mux muxer-properties="properties,streamable=true,fragment-duration=1000" async-finalize=true max-size-time=10000000000 send-keyframe-requests=true

 - generates fragmented files